name: You May Start Your Landing
Lore: 'Echo Base was no match for the Imperial war machine.',
Text: 'Deploy on table if 5th Marker also on table. During your control phase opponent loses 1 Force for each marker site you occupy with an AT-AT. Once per game, may take both Walker Garrison and 3rd Marker into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
